Class SnpEffAnnotatorRunnable

java.lang.Object
runnables.SnpEffAnnotatorRunnable
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.lang.Runnable
public final class SnpEffAnnotatorRunnable
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Runnable
Implementation of the Runnable interface to run SnpEff.

Runs SnpEff on one sample in a single thread.

Since:
2.0
Version:
2.0
Author:
Simon Hackl

      referenceName - String name of the reference to which respect the sample is analyzed.
